125. Tam dulcis sonus. The idea which is here expressed of the ⁸ music of the spheres ’ was a favourite one with the ancient philosophers. That the harmonicus order of the universe should produce a harmony of sound seemed to them natural, from the high place which they gave to musical harmony in their systems.
